      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHE WILL KICK (8) has a strong record this trip with five wins and two placings from 11 starts. In the money last time at this track (22.55) in a Grade 5, finishing a 6 length second. Has the ability and should feature. LAKOTA COURTNEY (7) held her own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only one length (22.49) behind Hey Bubba Louie at this track. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Leading chance. JET FUEL (1) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing fourth (30.43) at The Gardens in a Grade 5. Good beginner and aided by the inside draw. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. NOVEL (2) cannot be dismissed although new to this venue.",
